parameters: Akane! You ate my pudding again, didn't you?

Ah, was that Kanae's? I thought it was Hikaru's and ate
it... I'm sorry!
...If it's my pudding, you can eat it.
Really? Well then, go ahead and help yourself!
Hello. And Kanae, don't talk with your mouth full.

Wow, Hikaru looks like some kind of king. He's walking
around with a group of girls.
Hmm~ What should I do? A dancer?
Hey, what are we having for dinner?
Have you ever eaten pudding before?
That's an appetizer. Dessert is separate.
Hikaru has recently lost weight, but...

That's why, you should eat properly. Just try a little
harder, okay?
Even though it's been tough lately, I'm glad.
If you take care of your body and rest...

Huh? What are you talking about? Today is my turn! I'll
take a break starting from tomorrow!

Tomorrow is my turn. I think it would be better for me to take
a break starting the day after tomorrow.

It's my turn the day after tomorrow! Hehe, Hikaru can't
take a break.
Alright~ I brought a lot of healthy things for your body today.

The broccoli salad sauce is mixed with garlic and avocado.
Eat it together with eel tonight.
At the very least, my body needs time to absorb it.
Kanae doesn't know about that! I'll do it just like that!

It's embarrassing for a man to call his girlfriend Maman
or something like that, Hikaru. Let's give up, Mr.
Playboy.

I came home, but for some reason, I feel even more
tired.

Akane puts a small piece of chocolate in her mouth as if to
comfort me like that.

Akane, who has a broad mind, is the only one who truly
understands me.
They say chocolate is good for vitality.

Akane, licking her finger that touched my lips, while saying
so seductively.
There is no ally inside this house!
